s/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：覺得點為之 content farm？<code>反問</code><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌，你睇開嗰啲乜鳩嘢「壹讀」、「每日頭條」咪 content farm 囉柒頭 <code>讀心術</code><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你又知我嘅資訊源自𠵱啲 content farm？我嘅資源源自 Dr. Erickson，你 Google 都 search 到 <code>反讀心術</code><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：見你 post 啲嘢咁柒就知你睇開 content farm 啦 <code>扭曲</code><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：先假設一個人 post 啲嘢係你所認為嘅「柒」，佢就一定係睇開 content farm？ <code>糾正因果錯誤</code><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔同你嗌，總之 NLP 就係偽科學 <code>省略</code><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：從來心理學都唔係唯物科學，而係經驗學，你講嘅科學係咪指腦神經科學？另外 NLP 只係將幾個心理學大師、語言學專家嘅理論結合，包裝成一套課程 / 系統，所以如果我單純攞 Dr. Erickson 嘅 Milton Model 嚟講，咁又算唔算係偽心理學？ <code>反省略</code><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔知你講乜鳩，總之你連垃圾都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <code>一般化</code><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：既然一件垃圾肯同你理性討論咁耐，你係咪應該視𠵱件垃圾為珍寶？<code>引述 + 承接 + 反扭曲</code><br />\n<br />\n。。。"},{"pid":"13ffb8b3120cfec9cecaef8d73fa132bc7ee8a02","tid":1988813,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學到野"},{"pid":"a5f352de5b052dd9c411af233bcce0936abacf27","tid":1988813,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T06:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8e3f9d751c1c40604ff79640c2f55ed1865dcc","tid":1988813,"uid":13562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T06:18:51.000Z","msg":"LM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fbcb7e8c34ecc007339a74fc33f0efe38fbecf","tid":1988813,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"不過為咗支持連登仔可以更成熟學識「洗腦」而達到佢哋嘅正面目的（爭取民主自由），本窮狗會講多少少點樣可以加強「洗腦」嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實如果鍾意用 Milton Model  洗人腦，要先了解 Milton Model 嘅關鍵唔係嗰啲技巧，而係喺咩嘢腦波狀態下用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMilton Model 係一種騙子嘅語言技巧，當然你喺條友正常腦波下用，都會發揮到佢嘅效用，只係效果唔持久。（例如你想洗一件冇腦廢老由藍變黃，可能變黃咗一星期又變返藍）<br />\n<br />\n要達到好似騙子咁發揮最大嘅洗腦，可以嘗試喺被洗腦者以下狀態下落手：<br />\n1. 啱啱瞓醒 / 啱啱瞓梗覺但未瞓著<br />\n2. 傳銷式疲勞轟炸（Information Overflow）<br />\n3. 傳銷式人群壓力<br />\n4. 令當時人突然極到恐慌<br />\n5. 當時人感到極度平靜<br />\n<br />\n目的就係要當時人處於 alpha wave 狀態，閂咗佢個 critical thinking system，然後利用 Molton Model 下達潛意識命令<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果該藍絲廢老一早俾藍絲嘅 Milton Model 洗腦，我哋可以相反喺當時人正常 beta 腦波下一斷用 Meta Model 反問佢，糾正佢藍絲嘅錯誤價值觀，一樣可以達到藍變黃嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡而言之<br />\nMilton Model 喺 alpha 波下用<br />\nMeta Model 喺 beta 波下用<br />\n同樣可以達到改變信念系統嘅效果"},{"pid":"d35feaf954cb3790c97d2ec7366616cf9663e765","tid":1988813,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T06:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過為咗支持連登仔可以更成熟學識「洗腦」而達到佢哋嘅正面目的（爭取民主自由），本窮狗會講多少少點樣可以加強「洗腦」嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實如果鍾意用 Milton Model  洗人腦，要先了解 Milton Model 嘅關鍵唔係嗰啲技巧，而係喺咩嘢腦波狀態下用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMilton Model 係一種騙子嘅語言技巧，當然你喺條友正常腦波下用，都會發揮到佢嘅效用，只係效果唔持久。（例如你想洗一件冇腦廢老由藍變黃，可能變黃咗一星期又變返藍）<br />\n<br />\n要達到好似騙子咁發揮最大嘅洗腦<span style=\"color: red;\">效果</span>，可以嘗試喺被洗腦者以下狀態下落手：<br />\n1. 啱啱瞓醒 / 啱啱瞓梗覺但未瞓著<br />\n2. 傳銷式疲勞轟炸（Information Overflow）<br />\n3. 傳銷式人群壓力<br />\n4. 令當時人突然極到恐慌<br />\n5. 當時人感到極度平靜<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6. 專業人士包裝（學校教我哋要 trust professional）</span><br />\n<br />\n目的就係要當時人處於 alpha wave 狀態，閂咗佢個 critical thinking system，然後利用 <span style=\"color: red;\"> Milton</span> Model 下達潛意識命令<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果該藍絲廢老一早俾藍絲嘅 Milton Model 洗腦，我哋可以相反喺當時人正常 beta 腦波下<span style=\"color: red;\">不</span>斷用 Meta Model 反問佢，糾正佢藍絲嘅錯誤價值觀，一樣可以達到藍變黃嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡而言之<br />\nMilton Model 喺 alpha 波下用<br />\nMeta Model 喺 beta 波下用<br />\n同樣可以達到改變信念系統嘅效果</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a5c2548bdf8163d6a462225d9486fdadcfae5ebf","tid":1988813,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed040e0bc85a64935c8a62e54e2f4e6b677a64f9","tid":1988813,"uid":47475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:08:19.000Z","msg":"家吓真係要多啲呢啲技術post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔明或者唔同意都可以傾吓或者思考吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09efb1ed9a6ab58e775d8d2c853e59ef8a4b886f","tid":1988813,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed040e0bc85a64935c8a62e54e2f4e6b677a64f9","tid":1988813,"uid":47475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:08:19.000Z","msg":"家吓真係要多啲呢啲技術post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔明或者唔同意都可以傾吓或者思考吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"本人嘅八字係「偏印」型人，所以論吸收知識、學習能力可能會比其他人強<br />\n<br />\n但如果講到發揮技術嘅能力，可能我會比其他人弱，但希望幫到啲「食傷」勁嘅人學咗然後發揮出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e0c55208a1df82e5c13caee171537ef77f8381","tid":1988813,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T01:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1