.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c358099edbaed50afb2e69c7d5afc8d8d4c7e9f1","tid":1988813,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09efb1ed9a6ab58e775d8d2c853e59ef8a4b886f","tid":1988813,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed040e0bc85a64935c8a62e54e2f4e6b677a64f9","tid":1988813,"uid":47475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:08:19.000Z","msg":"家吓真係要多啲呢啲技術post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔明或者唔同意都可以傾吓或者思考吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"本人嘅八字係「偏印」型人，所以論吸收知識、學習能力可能會比其他人強<br />\n<br />\n但如果講到發揮技術嘅能力，可能我會比其他人弱，但希望幫到啲「食傷」勁嘅人學咗然後發揮出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T08:33:45.000Z","msg":"咁講喎<br />\n對五毛一樣無用<br />\n因為佢地只係負責哂大家時間心機"},{"pid":"2b03d9deaadf1cbe7ce7360f8af59e97021a6e06","tid":1988813,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7edcc021f5fb9d1ea2789a38c0e94f8beac23f0b","tid":1988813,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T08:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n連登不停標簽啲女人係雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一般化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T12:06:21.000Z","msg":"咁我哋要 study 吓係咪所有女人都有個「屄」價先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果可以 plot 到一個「屄」報價表嘅 normal distribution<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以證明大部分女人都係雞，但都唔可以證明所有女人都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋點定義雞？收兵攞著數嗰啲又算唔算係雞？"},{"pid":"e3453f5b6b5b033ec81aaa514f05ee5b49eb04eb","tid":1988813,"uid":168567,"like":2,